text: Progress () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Tlyaumbetovsky Selsoviet, Kugarchinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 11 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 49 km from Mrakovo, 7 km from Tlyaumbetovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kugarchinsky District
title: Progress, Kugarchinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
